==Starting out==
===Inspecting the dwarf===
* '''Player:''' How do I protect you I wonder....
* '''Aris:''' To protect our short angry friend from the culinaromancer's magics, I suggest that you seek out his father within the mountain tunnel that he guards.
* '''Aris:''' His fondness for rock cakes could prove key in freeing him.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the cook===
* '''Player:''' Can we talk about what happened in the dining room?
* '''Cook:''' Wow! You were incredible! The way you defeated the Culinaromancer, you made it seem so easy!
* '''Player:''' So... I don't suppose you can remember how I defeated him can you?
* '''Cook:''' Of course! Which bit can't you remember doing?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Protecting the Dwarf}}
