==Below White Wolf Mountain==
===Talking to "An old Dwarf"===
* '''Player:''' ...son...time bubble...culinaromancer...freeze...rockcakes!
* '''An old Dwarf:''' ...
* '''An old Dwarf:''' I have absolutely no clue what you are on about. Sit down, catch your breath and explain please!
* '''Player:''' Ok. Your son, the one who guards the tunnel entrance?
* '''An old Dwarf:''' Oh aye. Good lad he is.
* '''Player:''' Well he's at a special meeting and he's frozen by the culinaromancer!
* '''An old Dwarf:''' Ok... you lost me again. I just got back from visitin' him up top, he's fine.
* '''Player:''' He's in a TIME BUBBLE!
* '''An old Dwarf:''' Oh that. No no, he's quite ok. That was last week.
* '''Player:''' I need your rock cakes to free him from it.
* '''Rohak:''' You're delusional. Never would old Rohak give away his special recipe, not for all the golden nectar from the Rising Sun!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak again===
* '''Rohak:''' I would never give away me special rock cake recipe, not for all the golden nectar from the Rising Sun!
* {{tact|end}}

