==Getting the recipe==
===Talking to Rohak with Asgoldian ale in inventory===
* '''Player:''' Here, have a drink.
* {{tbox|pic=Asgoldian ale detail.png|You hand the ale to the dwarf who slurps it with a noise of a thousand seals celebrating a rain of fish.}}
* '''Rohak:''' Is that what I think it is?
* '''Player:''' Maybe!
* '''Rohak:''' That's from the Rising Sun, the barmaid there will never tell me the recipe she uses. It's divine!
* '''Player:''' Speaking of recipes....
* '''Rohak:''' No! I shwears I'll never tell...
* {{tbox|pic=Asgoldian ale detail.png|The dwarf nurses the very last drops of the pint as if he'd really like more.}}

===Talking to Rohak with a second Asgoldian ale in inventory===
* '''Player:''' Here, have another.
* '''Rohak:''' Don't mind if I do!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak with a third Asgoldian ale in inventory===
* '''Player:''' I think you deserve another pint.
* '''Rohak:''' Don't mind if I do!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak with a fourth Asgoldian ale in inventory===
* '''Player:''' I'm sure another pint will go down nicely.
* '''Rohak:''' Don't mind if I do!
* {{tbox|Several beers later....}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak again once he is sufficiently drunk===
* '''Rohak:''' Ahhh, yer me besht mate... mate.
* '''Player:''' You're a good friend Rohak, do you think you could do me a favour?
* '''Rohak:''' Fer you [player]? Fer you I'd... I'd... shlide down a shlope of thishtlesh wif no 'elmet on!
* '''Player:''' I don't need you to do that ... friend. Just something as simple as baking me some of your wonderful rock cakes. Hmm? For your good friend?
* '''Rohak:''' Fer you! Anyfin'! Fer a price of course!
* '''Player:''' Good. I'm sure I have some gold somewhere!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to a sober Rohak===
* '''Player:''' How much gold do you want to make the cake?
* '''Rohak:''' WHAT?! That wasn't a dream? Oh my aching head...
* '''Player:''' No, not a dream, you agreed to make me your special rock cake, for a fee.
* '''Rohak:''' Oh.
* '''Rohak:''' 100 gold, no less!
* {{tcond|If the player doesn't have enough money}}
** '''Player:''' Maybe I should have some more money with me, he did say he'd want payment...
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has enough money}}
** '''Rohak:''' Also... you'll need to get the ingredients too. Milk, flour, egg and bowl of water, mind it's a bowl and not a dirty bucket.
** {{tbox|pic=coins 250 detail.png|You hand over 100 gold.}}
** '''Player:''' You didn't say I'd have to run around... but ok! Milk, flour, egg, bowl of water....I'll be back!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak again===
* {{tcond|If the player has none of the items}}
** '''Rohak:''' Have you forgotten the ingredients list? I'll need an egg, a pot of flour, a bucket of milk and a bowl of water to make these cakes for you.
** '''Player:''' Ok, I'll see about getting them.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player only has some of the items}}
** '''Player:''' I have found some of the things you asked for:
** {{tact|The following dialogue will change depending on what items the player has:}}
** '''Player:''' [I have the egg/I don't have an egg, I'll look for some chickens], [I have a pot of flour/I don't have a pot of flour, but I'll investigate the windmills], [I have the bucket of milk/I don't have any milk but I'll check out the cows], [I have the bowl of water!/I don't have a bowl of water].
** '''Rohak:''' That's all well and good...but come back when you have all the ingredients. You're lucky Dwarves stick to their word else I might not make these cakes for you.
** '''Player:''' Okay okay I'll get right on it! Keep your beard on!
** '''Rohak:''' What did you say?
** '''Player:''' N..n...nothing honest!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has all the items}}
** '''Player:''' I have all the items you asked for...is that it? I could make these!
** '''Rohak:''' No you couldn't, there's a special ingredient, but I'm not going to tell you what it is!
** '''Player:''' Well... here's the ingredients anyway.
** {{tbox|pic=egg detail.png|You hand over the ingredients and watch the dwarf make the cake.}}
** {{tbox|Rohak places the cake on the table.}}
** '''Rohak:''' There, as good as my word. Hot rock cakes to my special recipe.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Rohak after he has made the rock cake===
* '''Rohak:''' Got any use out of that rock cake I made you [player]?
* {{tcond|If the player still has the rock cake}}
** '''Player:''' Not yet but I will. I'm going to save your son.
** '''Rohak:''' I keep tellin you, he's fine!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has lost the rock cake}}
** '''Player:''' I appear to have lost it somewhere, can you make me another?
** '''Rohak:''' I suppose so, but you'll need all the ingredients like last time.
** {{tcond|If the player has none of the items}}
