===Attempting to free the dwarf with a hot rock cake===
* '''Aris:''' STOP! What do you think you're doing!
* '''Aris:''' You can't feed him red hot rock cakes! You'll kill him! Find a way to cool them down.
* '''Player:''' Oh, ok, I'll find a way to cool them down then.
* '''Aris:''' I hear there's a rather chilly reception on top of a rather icey mountain.
* {{tact|end}}

===Cooling the rock cake by killing an icefiend===
* {{mes|The dying breath of the icefiend cools your hot rock cake.}}

===Cooling the rock cake by wearing ice gloves===
* {{mes|Your ice gloves cool the hot rock cake as you pick it up.}}

